name: Exemption of voting stock from registration
text:
Membership stock or membership certificates under section 421C‑3(a), or share or membership capital of any association organized under or existing prior to passage of this chapter shall be included as exempt securities under section 485-4. [L 1982, c 97, pt of §2]
 
Note
 
  Effective date of L 1982, c 97 is May 15, 1982.
